got here from people.

12:03.607 --> 12:06.344
Yeah. If there's pigs, there's people.

12:06.444 --> 12:11.557
Okay, cadets. Like I said,
this island's probably uninhabited.

12:11.657 --> 12:16.103
- We don't know. We've gotta explore.
- DARK-HAIRED BOY: There's a lot to do.

12:16.203 --> 12:22.235
