Nobody knows we're here.
They know where we were going.

12:36.349 --> 12:40.503
But they don't know where we are.
We never got where we were going.

12:40.603 --> 12:44.633
- SMALL BOY: Where were we going?
- We were going home.

12:44.733 --> 12:46.682
(GROANING)

12:48.820 --> 12:51.389
DARK-HAIRED BOY:
I'm sure they're looking.

12:51.489 --> 12:55.060
